Clerics who take the Storm domain embody the essence of the tempest, and are granted spells that reflect their turbulent nature.

<b>Domain Special Ability and Bonus Spells</b>
- Resist Energy: Electricity: The cleric is resistant to the fury of the thunderous sky.

- The cleric gains access to the following spells at the specified spell level: <i>Gust of Wind (2), Call Lightning (3), Ice Storm (5), Chain Lightning(7)</i>.